港警務處前助理處長Angus Stevenson Hamilton發出電郵，查詢他會否願意主動撤回「皇家」二字及如何回應信件的批評。協會秘書Barry Jones其後代會長回覆，稱初步的查問令他們傾向相信信件並不真實（Initial enquiries tend to make us believe that the letter is not genuine），他們已向上議院查詢，強調若發現信件是偽造，將會向英國警方舉報。不過，Jones並無回應記者最初的問題。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》隨即以電郵向聯署的議員查詢信件的真實性，其中自由民主黨黨鞭Lord Alton of Liverpool、工黨議員Baroness Lister of Burtersett及獨立議員Lord Hylton數小時內即回覆記者，3人均確認信件是真實，由他們5名議員發予英女皇。記者獲確認後再向協會查詢，暫未獲覆。<br />\n對於英女皇會否褫奪相關銜頭，Lord Alton of Liverpool稱不會猜度女皇的決定，但強調女皇會基於政府大臣的建議行事，所以他們才會把信件抄送外交及聯邦事務大臣藍韜文，其同事亦會與外交部保持溝通。Baroness Lister of Burtersett坦言並不預期英女皇會同意他們的建議，但稱聯署是為了表達對香港警察對待示威者手段的深切關注；Lord Hylton則說不知道英女皇會否答應，但認為值得一試（it is worth asking）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191204/large/1575474404_4451.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575474404_4451.png&h=9796d874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191205/60342971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342971&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1ezbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=ce9ea70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342971&h=c2bfbd75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191205/60342971</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:04:33.000Z","msg":"Popo 第一時間話封野假仲要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係同一個派別同血統，永遠唔覺得自己錯。"},{"pid":"e62343886597578753dbcf4228ca7a0977b63d75","tid":1769312,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:04:47.000Z","msg":"佢地係未真係咁平行世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同葉劉一撚樣以為外國做鳩你起假"},{"pid":"8ff08191b44037846b99feaf3722535331a4f4d1","tid":1769312,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep